[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1189","title":"Netscape Navigator/Communicator 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator/Communicator 4.7 在处理 URL 时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当 URL 中 ? 后的参数长度超过缓冲区边界时，会触发栈溢出。远程攻击者可构造包含超长参数的恶意 URL（指向 .asp、.cgi、.html 或 .pl 文件），诱使用户访问后导致浏览器崩溃拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98 平台上的 Netscape 4.7 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1189"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Netscape Navigator/Communicator 至 4.73 及以上版本，该版本修复了长 URL 参数导致的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，建议在 Web 服务器端过滤超长 URL 请求参数，限制 ? 后参数长度不超过 1024 字节。鉴于该浏览器已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/36306","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/36608","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/822","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7884"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1162","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1162.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1527","title":"Sun NetBeans Java IDE Web 服务器 IP 访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"Sun NetBeans Java IDE 内置的 HTTP 服务器（见于 NetBeans Developer 3.0 Beta 及 Forte Community Edition 1.0 Beta）未能正确依据配置中的 IP 地址访问控制规则限制访问。该内置 Web 服务默认随 IDE 启动并监听本地网络端口，攻击者可构造请求从任意远程 IP 地址绕过既定的 IP 白名单限制，在未获授权的情况下访问本应受限的服务器资源与开发数据。由于配置中的 IP 限制机制失效，任何能够与目标主机建立网络连接的远程攻击者均可远程利用此缺陷，造成信息泄露与未授权访问，CVSS 基础评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1527"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:37.903","remediation":"升级至 NetBeans 正式稳定版而非 Developer 3.0 Beta 或 Forte Community Edition 1.0 Beta，以彻底消除内置 HTTP 服务器的 IP 访问控制缺陷。如短期内无法升级，应在 IDE 项目设置中将 HTTP Server 的 Enable 选项设为 False，或在全局设置中移除 HTTP Server 模块，并建议在防火墙层面阻断 TCP 8082 端口以阻止外部未授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94338883114254&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/816","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/37cec437f4ca5dbafb8ef4c4921c71da1b289b8f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1527.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1527","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1527.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1527.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vf3q-mq2p-f2jx/GHSA-vf3q-mq2p-f2jx.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/netbeans.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/816/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1527.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--cbc4e1aa-8edf-422c-9099-8d5438e57ea5.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1162.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0911","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1058","title":"Vermillion FTP Daemon 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务连续发送多个超长的 CWD（切换工作目录）命令，触发服务端缓冲区溢出，进而导致拒绝服务，并可能执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响运行 VFTPD 1.23 的所有服务器，攻击者无需任何凭据，仅需连接至 21 端口即可发起利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1058"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.050","remediation":"立即停用并卸载存在漏洞的 Vermillion FTP Daemon (VFTPD) 1.23，替换为仍在维护的开源 FTP 服务（如 vsftpd、ProFTPD）至最新版本；若必须短期保留，可在边界防火墙限制仅允许受信 IP 访问 TCP 21 端口，并部署入侵检测规则阻断包含超长 CWD 命令的 FTP 请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94329968617085&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94337185023159&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/818","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3543","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1058","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1058.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/V/vftpd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000890.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d60c1d6c-3fba-4fac-9858-a021833ded43.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0832","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0999","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9148,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10833}}","description":"Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 的 Tabular Data Stream (TDS) 数据包解析存在验证不足的问题。攻击者远程发送特制的畸形 TDS 报文，可触发服务端异常，导致 SQL Server 服务崩溃并进入拒绝服务状态。该漏洞影响 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 及 7.0 SP1 版本，攻击者无需身份验证即可轻易利用实现服务中断，严重影响数据库服务可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0999"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.610","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft SQL Server 7.0 Service Pack 2（SP2）或更高版本以修复 TDS 协议解析缺陷。如暂无法升级，可在边界防火墙或 IPS 上过滤并丢弃发往 1433 端口的畸形 TDS 数据包，限制仅允许可信 IP 访问数据库端口，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248749","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/817","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-059","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19638","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0999.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0999","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c3675993ac058501ff8575bd07a9ca0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0999.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0999.md","https://github.com/dependency-check/DependencyCheck/blob/7dcfc0737c21744b423c2198ae979003c2eb67e2/core/src/main/resources/dependencycheck-base-suppression.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v/GHSA-cj38-2rjc-pv2v.json","https://github.com/morpheuslord/CVE-llm_dataset/blob/91b337d05c623a68829de977c2b1ae6c0f91702b/README.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0999.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0832.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0617","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0831","title":"Linux Kernel Syslog 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 syslogd 守护进程在处理网络连接时存在拒绝服务漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发起大量并发连接请求消耗系统资源，触发 syslogd 进程崩溃或系统响应变慢，导致日志服务长时间不可用。该漏洞影响运行 syslogd 的各类 Linux 发行版，攻击条件简单，攻击者仅需使用脚本持续向目标 syslog 端口发送连接请求即可复现利用，无需任何权限或凭证。攻击成功后，系统将丧失日志记录能力，影响安全审计、故障排查及事件溯源，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0831"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.923","remediation":"建议将 Linux 内核升级至 2.2.13 及以上版本（含 syslogd 修复补丁），或应用各发行版对应安全更新（如 Red Hat 的 syslogd 补丁包）。如无法立即升级，可在 /etc/syslog.conf 中限制 syslogd 监听来源，使用防火墙规则限制可发起 syslog 连接的客户端 IP，并降低 syslog 服务并发连接上限以缓解拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/809","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f56f639de76f94fc0aef783754a3de16fea7357b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0831.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0831","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0831.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/be19cdaa6196942fd4096a42a1eaf047a8584298/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0831.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-3cgm-rhf4-87qm/GHSA-3cgm-rhf4-87qm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0831.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3734eac1-0b8f-4454-909e-1af399633844.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d8232fe3e2556046ab374e149ecb1f50a314b074/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1124","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1124.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1475","title":"ProFTPD mod_sqlpw 密码泄露漏洞","description":"ProFTPD 1.2 在编译启用 mod_sqlpw 模块时存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。该模块会将用户认证密码明文记录到系统 wtmp 日志文件中，本地攻击者可通过执行 last 等命令读取 wtmp 日志获取其他用户的明文密码，进而利用获取的密码提升权限或横向移动。该漏洞影响 ProFTPD 1.2 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，攻击复杂度低，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1475"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19","updated":"1999-11-19","remediation":"升级 ProFTPD 至 1.2.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复 mod_sqlpw 将用户密码明文写入 wtmp 日志的问题。如无法升级，可卸载 mod_sqlpw 模块或限制 wtmp 日志文件的读取权限（chmod 640 /var/log/wtmp），仅允许 root 用户访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1124.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0987","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9104,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10785}}","description":"Windows NT 系统在域用户登录时未能正确处理域名的边界情况。当域用户使用在域名末尾带有空格的域名登录到域时，系统无法正确下载并应用系统策略（System Policy），导致安全策略被绕过。该漏洞影响使用域环境且依赖系统策略进行安全管控的 Windows NT 系统，攻击条件为攻击者需诱导或控制域用户以带尾随空格的域名登录域控制器。利用方式上，攻击者可通过构造特殊的登录域名使目标主机跳过应有的安全策略限制，从而削弱系统安全防护、提升本地权限或绕过既定的访问控制策略，造成安全配置失效的风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0987"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.090","remediation":"建议升级到 Windows 2000 或更高版本，并安装 Microsoft 发布的安全补丁（如 MS99-024 补丁包 Q246045）。若无法升级，请确保域用户登录时不在域名末尾添加空格，并在域控制器配置严格的域名验证策略防止尾随空格登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237923","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0987","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0987.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/72b66ad516faec962399c4214c080517aebc4c11/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9vg4-j6g2-gw83/GHSA-9vg4-j6g2-gw83.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000886.txt","https://github.com/chandanbn/notes/blob/90eb64532f7259c55e5531dfc2726d810d17ef6e/cve5-validation-errors-Jan27.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0528","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0793","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9166,\"outputTokens\":14,\"totalTokens\":10844}}","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 和 4.0.1 版本中存在 JavaScript URL 重定向漏洞 (MS99-043)，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页将数据重定向至 JavaScript 小程序，从而读取用户本地文件系统中的任意文件。该漏洞源于 IE 对 JavaScript URL 重定向处理不当，攻击者只需诱导用户访问精心构造的恶意页面，即可在无需用户交互的情况下窃取本地敏感文件。该漏洞影响 IE 5.0 和 4.0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 2.6（低危），攻击复杂度较高，需用户访问恶意页面触发。Microsoft 已在 MS99-043 安全公告中发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0793"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.173","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 SP1 或更高版本并应用 Microsoft 安全更新 MS02-018，建议同时更换为 Chrome/Firefox 等现代浏览器。如无法立即升级，可通过注册表禁用 JavaScript 协议处理，并在 Windows 防火墙阻止文件访问流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-043","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19559","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0793.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0793.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0793","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0793.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0793.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mj4p-5fc7-96gj/GHSA-mj4p-5fc7-96gj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0793.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0528.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1155","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1155.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1519","title":"Gene6 G6 FTP Server 2.0 超长用户名或密码导致资源耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Gene6 G6 FTP Server 2.0 在处理 FTP 登录过程的用户名与密码参数时，未对输入长度进行合理限制。远程攻击者可在未认证的情况下，向 FTP 服务发送超长的用户名或超长的密码请求，导致服务器端分配异常资源并耗尽系统资源，最终使 FTP 服务停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击条件仅是能够与目标 21 端口建立网络连接，利用门槛低、危害集中于服务可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1519"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-17","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级到 Gene6 G6 FTP Server 后续修复版本；如无法立即升级，应在防火墙或边界设备上限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 21 端口，并在 FTP 服务配置中对用户名与密码长度设置上限、拒绝畸形超长请求，同时启用最大连接数与连接速率限制以缓解资源耗尽风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94286244700573&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/805","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3513"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1155.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1980","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1980.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1508","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9201,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10886}}","description":"Tektronix Phaser系列网络打印机（740/750/750DP/840/930）中的PhaserLink Web服务器存在严重漏洞，攻击者可通过直接调用未记录的URL（如ncl_items.html和ncl_subjects.html）获取管理员密码，进而获得打印机完全控制权。此漏洞影响840.0及更早版本，攻击者无需身份验证即可远程利用，攻击路径简单直接。该漏洞CVSS评分达到10.0，表明其风险极其严重。补救措施包括升级到安全版本，禁用未记录URL，并加强管理员认证机制。修复后应确保所有内部功能URL都经过适当验证，并删除任何潜在的隐藏漏洞，导致目标打印机完全被攻陷。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1508"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:35.480","remediation":"建议立即升级 Tektronix PhaserLink 固件至 840.1 或更高版本（联系 Tektronix 技术支持获取固件）；若无法升级，请在防火墙/ACL 限制打印机 Web 管理端口（80/443）仅允许受信管理 IP 访问，并修改默认管理员密码；建议将打印机置于隔离 VLAN，禁止直接暴露在互联网或办公网段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94286041430870&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/806","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19632","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d7a64f7f43d1af6189d4f7237515b997555b777/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1508.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1508","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1508.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1508.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-57xx-x4mm-8j32/GHSA-57xx-x4mm-8j32.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/d1d5df31afb4307aa17e44603eab07fbdaf94076/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/ncl_items.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/806/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1508.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1980.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1980.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1980.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1177","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1177.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1549","title":"Lynx 网页浏览器 LYNXOPTIONS: URL 配置篡改远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Lynx 2.x 浏览器未能正确区分内部 HTML 与外部 HTML，本地攻击者可从临时文件中读取本应保密的隐藏表单值，进而构造特殊的 LYNXOPTIONS: URL。当受害用户在本地运行 Lynx 并访问该恶意 URL 时，Lynx 会被诱导修改用户配置文件（如 lynx.cfg）并据此执行攻击者指定的命令。该漏洞影响 Lynx 2.x 系列本地用户环境，攻击需本地访问权限及诱导用户访问恶意链接或文件，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1549"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:41.687","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.8.2 及以上版本（修复了对内部/外部 HTML 的区分缺陷）。如无法立即升级，应限制临时文件权限避免本地用户读取 LYNXOPTIONS 相关临时文件，并在浏览器配置中禁用 LYNXOPTIONS: 协议处理，避免通过恶意 URL 修改配置文件或执行命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94286509804526&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/804","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1549.json","https://github.com/kenhuangus/llm-wiki/blob/d2bd485921f6c7b6071afbb389f44ab8e4e83c69/wiki/security/cve/cve-1999-1549.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1549","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1549.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a20296d4b03dbd5c5991115b8296a9f2b947592/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1549.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cgjq-p4q9-cfj7/GHSA-cgjq-p4q9-cfj7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/804/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-346.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1177.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1115","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1115.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1457","title":"thttpd HTTP Server 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"thttpd HTTP 服务器 2.04-31 之前版本中的 tdate_parse 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长日期字符串触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 thttpd 2.04-31 之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至 2.04-31 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1457"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:28.903","remediation":"升级 thttpd 至 2.04-31 或更高版本，该版本修复了 tdate_parse 函数对超长日期字符串的缓冲区边界检查问题。如无法升级，建议在 thttpd 前端部署反向代理（如 Nginx）过滤异常请求头，或替换为维护中的轻量级 HTTP 服务器（如 lighttpd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_30.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1115.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0903","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1051","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 路径遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 脚本在默认配置下允许将任意目录作为附件目录，且仅对 /etc/ 目录做了访问限制。远程攻击者可通过 reply_message_attach 附件参数构造包含路径遍历序列（如 ../../../etc/passwd）的请求，读取服务器上的任意文件内容，造成敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1051"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.223","remediation":"修改 FormHandler.cgi 脚本的默认配置，将 reply_message_attach 参数允许的附件目录严格限定在 Web 根目录下的专用附件目录，并在代码中显式过滤包含 '../' 等路径遍历序列的输入。同时移除对 /etc/ 目录的单一限制，改为仅允许白名单目录。升级到更新的表单处理脚本或应用官方安全补丁。在 Web 服务器层面对 cgi-bin 目录设置访问控制，仅允许可信来源访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2aa0c2dcb1730150467a1bc57cd9b2ece96310af/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1051","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/419b5e73717835e3c91c8f5fe969933e4b2e142e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88494/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--beb8e606-6327-4a7d-9502-dbb547f2795a.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0903.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0903.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1777","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1777.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1190","title":"Admiral Systems EmailClub POP3 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Admiral Systems EmailClub 1.05 版本 POP3 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含超长 \"From\" 头部的恶意电子邮件触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 EmailClub 所有用户，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1190"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-15","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品（Admiral Systems EmailClub）已停止维护，厂商不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至现代、持续维护的邮件服务器软件（如 Dovecot、Cyrus IMAP），并关闭 POP3 服务的外部网络访问以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securiteam.com/exploits/E-MailClub__FROM__remote_buffer_overflow.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/801","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19621"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19621"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1777.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1163","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1163.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1528","title":"普软公司 Netware客户端 for MacOS 继承NDS漏洞","description":"ProSoft Netware Client 5.12 在 Macintosh MacOS 9 上存在会话管理漏洞。当用户注销系统时，客户端不会自动将用户从 NDS 树中注销，导致 NDS 会话保持活动状态且未受保护。这允许同一系统的其他用户访问未受保护的 NDS 会话，可能导致未授权访问网络资源。该漏洞影响运行 MacOS 9 且安装 ProSoft Netware Client 5.12 的系统，CVSS 评分 4.6（中等严重度），攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限才能利用该会话劫持漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1528"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:38.030","remediation":"升级 ProSoft Netware Client 至 5.12 以上版本，或安装厂商当时提供的安全补丁。如无法升级，用户注销系统前应手动断开 NDS 连接（在 Netware 客户端中选择注销 NDS），并加强 MacOS 9 系统的物理访问控制，防止未授权用户接触已登录终端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94261444428430&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/794","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/37cec437f4ca5dbafb8ef4c4921c71da1b289b8f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1528.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1528","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1528.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1528.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vj7j-f273-546c/GHSA-vj7j-f273-546c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/794/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1528.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/deb35dfa9d2a852a9e74a49ee9f005902a507596/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1163.toml"}]